age here on Udemy and connect with me on LinkedIn, check out my profile for other courses.</strong></p>\r\n<p>We also have a 30-day money back guarantee, so you can try out the course for an entire month, risk-free!</p>\r\n<p>Always keep learning!</p>\r\n<p>Jose</p></div>', 11.99, 0, 1, 1, '2021-01-13 01:52:50', '2021-01-15 07:49:21', 4, 0, NULL);
